  </para>
</solution>
</exercise><exercise id="eip-72"><problem id="eip-401">
  <para id="eip-22">
    The burden of proof in a threatened trade secret misappropriation case lies with whom?
<preformat id="eip-id7814213">
         A. The trade secret owner
         B. The former employee who leaves to go work for a competitor
         C. The competitor, who must prove he did no wrong by hiring the ex-employee
</preformat>
  </para>
</problem>

<solution id="eip-404">
